{"id":82359,"title":"Recurrent parotitis of childhood or juvenile recurrent parotitis--a review and report of two cases.","abstract":"Recurrent parotitis of childhood is an uncommon condition which affects children of variable age. The condition may be misdiagnosed so delaying treatment. These two case reports highlight the variable signs and symptoms of this unusual condition and the value of ultrasound as an aid to diagnosis.This is to improve awareness of recurrent parotitis of childhood and aid early diagnosis.","date":"2014-03-19","categories":"Stomatognathic Diseases","split":"train","url":"http://www.ncbi.nlm.nih.gov/pubmed/24640481","annotations":[{"name":"Ultrasound","weight":0.739806,"wikipedia_article":"http://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Ultrasound"},{"name":"Diagnosis","weight":0.703282,"wikipedia_article":"http://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Diagnosis"},{"name":"Medical diagnosis","weight":0.697406,"wikipedia_article":"http://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Medical_diagnosis"},{"name":"Symptom","weight":0.632823,"wikipedia_article":"http://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Symptom"},{"name":"Medical sign","weight":0.559736,"wikipedia_article":"http://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Medical_sign"},{"name":"Therapy","weight":0.558261,"wikipedia_article":"http://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Therapy"},{"name":"Medical error","weight":0.170177,"wikipedia_article":"http://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Medical_error"},{"name":"Case report","weight":0.107046,"wikipedia_article":"http://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Case_report"},{"name":"Awareness","weight":0.0391252,"wikipedia_article":"http://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Awareness"},{"name":"Parotitis","weight":0.0297972,"wikipedia_article":"http://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Parotitis"},{"name":"Childhood","weight":0.0276227,"wikipedia_article":"http://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Childhood"},{"name":"Recurrent neural network","weight":0.0168623,"wikipedia_article":"http://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Recurrent_neural_network"},{"name":"Minor (law)","weight":0.0147415,"wikipedia_article":"http://en.wi